1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,600
What if deep-sea diving could make you feel drunk?

2
00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:08,400
This phenomenon is called nitrogen narcosis — a potential risk for divers.

3
00:00:08,400 --> 00:00:10,400
As divers descend, pressure increases.

4
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:12,400
More nitrogen enters the bloodstream.

5
00:00:12,400 --> 00:00:13,200
Things get...

6
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:13,600
hazy.

7
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:16,400
Symptoms range from euphoria to impaired judgment.

8
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:18,000
Some even report hallucinations.

9
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:22,000
But here's the twist: not everyone reacts the same way.

10
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:23,200
It remains unpredictable.

11
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:25,200
Stay informed about diving safety!

12
00:00:25,200 --> 00:00:28,000
Like and follow for more science insights.
